<text x="70" y="160" fill="#2D3748" font-family="serif" font-size="16" font-weight="600">
Systematic Environmental Impact Assessment
</text>

<text x="70" y="200" fill="#4A5568" font-family="serif" font-size="14">
The methodology includes systematic approaches to environmental impact assessment
</text>
<text x="70" y="220" fill="#4A5568" font-family="serif" font-size="14">
and community consultation. These approaches ensure comprehensive evaluation
</text>
<text x="70" y="240" fill="#4A5568" font-family="serif" font-size="14">
