</text>

<text x="70" y="310" fill="#2D3748" font-family="serif" font-size="16" font-weight="600">
Community Consultation Integration
</text>

<text x="70" y="350" fill="#4A5568" font-family="serif" font-size="14">
Community consultation is embedded as a core component of the assessment
</text>
<text x="70" y="370" fill="#4A5568" font-family="serif" font-size="14">
methodology, ensuring that local knowledge and concerns are systematically
</text>
<text x="70" y="390" fill="#4A5568" font-family="serif" font-size="14">
incorporated into environmental planning decisions and impact evaluations.
</text>

<text x="70" y="440" fill="#2D3748" font-family="serif" font-size="16" font-weight="600">
Assessment Protocols and Standards
</text>

<text x="70" y="480" fill="#4A5568" font-family="serif" font-size="14">
